g Partner",{"label":575,"slug":576},"More on sustainability","sustainability","Floema® produces sustainable signage and equipment and offers durable, low maintenance solutions that integrate perfectly into the landscape, based on ecological raw materials.\n\nOur products are an important resource to enhance the heritage, urban environment, landscape and culture of any region.",[579],{"alt":580,"extension":76,"height":581,"hotspot":17,"type":20,"uid":582,"url":583,"width":584},"Berlengas Island, Portugal",1386,"e240a0ce2ee7","https://cdn.sanity.io/images/535lnz3g/production/f4f6a9547e8e40bd32975ab1052e2c7428226353-1328x1386.jpg",1328,"We think outdoor furniture should look and feel good while doing good for our planet",{"_type":587,"workflow":588},"workflowOverview",[589,597,604],{"description":590,"mediaAsset":591,"title":593},"Our products are designed to guarantee functionality and viability",[592],{"alt":593,"extension":76,"height":331,"hotspot":17,"type":20,"uid":594,"url":595,"width":596},"We design","145208bc11ac","https://cdn.sanity.io/images/535lnz3g/production/4c1a919b5e7601c1bf188b28c2cdf4aef3d228f2-1054x600.jpg",1054,{"description":598,"mediaAsset":599,"title":601},"Ensuring the technical and aesthetic aspects stay unaltered",[600],{"alt":601,"extension":76,"height":331,"hotspot":17,"type":20,"uid":602,"url":603,"width":596},"We build","aaf922520758","https://cdn.sanity.io/images/535lnz3g/production/fb095c31eb4ea6ce292e009ff8fd64ca958c8856-1054x600.jpg",{"description":605,"mediaAsset":606,"title":608},"Every solution is crafted to endure, with minimal environmental impact",[607],{"alt":608,"extension":76,"height":331,"hotspot":17,"type":20,"uid":609,"url":610,"width":596},"We implement","27369205547f","https://cdn.sanity.io/images/535lnz3g/production/6c9ebc51108f425c4888cf320e2698cf7a713f38-1054x600.jpg",{"_type":612,"title":613},"lowerTagline","Made to last, designed to endure.",1778864770509]